* A class for representing UNIX credentials passed via ancillary data
 * on UNIX domain sockets. See "man 7 unix" on a desktop linux distro.

variables.name: pid
variables.comment: pid of process. root peers may lie.

variables.name: uid
variables.comment: uid of process. root peers may lie.

variables.name: gid
variables.comment: gid of process. root peers may lie.
